      "width": 1192.4,
      "height": 18.75,
      "fontSize": 15,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "text": "Five layers \u00b7 one allocator tick \u00b7 the two-sided agentic economy:  x402 (buy data + GET PAID)  \u00b7  ERC-8004 (on-chain identity)  \u00b7  CMC (data)",
      "originalText": "Five layers \u00b7 one allocator tick \u00b7 the two-sided agentic economy:  x402 (buy data + GET PAID)  \u00b7  ERC-8004 (on-chain identity)  \u00b7  CMC (data)",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
