      "width": 512.6800000000001,
      "height": 55.0,
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "text": "SOLID arrow  \u2192   primary flow (down the stack \u00b7 left\u2192right within a plane)\nDASHED arrow      side feed / governs / risk-budget / ROADMAP\n\u24b6 = off-page 'continue here'    \u00b7    diamond = decision / guard\nreturn codes:   0 = ok   \u00b7   1 = drawdown HALT   \u00b7   2 = skip tick",
      "originalText": "SOLID arrow  \u2192   primary flow (down the stack \u00b7 left\u2192right within a plane)\nDASHED arrow      side feed / governs / risk-budget / ROADMAP\n\u24b6 = off-page 'continue here'    \u00b7    diamond = decision / guard\nreturn codes:   0 = ok   \u00b7   1 = drawdown HALT   \u00b7   2 = skip tick",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
